Geometry Cyl
    Name CylZ_Mesh
    R 0 5 1
    Z 0 {cyl_height} 400


Filter
    Name Protons
    Z == 1
    A == 1
Filter
    Name Primaries
    Z == 1
    A == 1
    GEN == 0
Filter
    Name Secondary_protons
    Z == 1
    A == 1
    GEN >= 1

Output
    Filename z_profile.bdo
    Geo CylZ_Mesh
    Quantity Dose  
    Quantity Fluence Protons 
    Quantity Fluence Primaries 
    Quantity Fluence Secondary_protons 
    Quantity dLET Protons
    Quantity dLET Primaries
    Quantity dLET Secondary_protons
